                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170219-115-off639 t18170219-115-cd640"></join>, one handkerchief, value 2s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18170219-115-victim910" type="victimName">
                           John 
